vine.math.vector

Class Vec2f

  • java.lang.Object
    • vine.math.vector.Vec2f
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MutableVec2f

    public class Vec2f
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a mathematical vector 2d and performs transformations on this object with its methods. Complete thread-safe.
    Author:
    Steffen
